                <lg type="stanza">
                    <l>The Body grows without -</l>
                    <l>The more convenient way - </l>
                    <l>That if the Spirit - like<app type="division"><lem><lb/></lem></app>
 to hide </l>
                    <l>It's<add type="alternate" extent="Temple">Closet</add>
 Temple stands, alway, </l>
                </lg>
                <lg type="stanza">
                    <l>Ajar - secure - inviting -</l>
                    <l>It never did betray </l>
                    <l>The Soul that asked it's<app type="division"><lem><lb/></lem></app>
 shelter </l>
                    <l>In<add type="alternate" extent="solemn">timid -</add>
 solemn honesty </l>
                </lg>

            </div>     
